WEBVTT

00:00.225 --> 00:02.195
This is iPhone 6s.

00:02.327 --> 00:04.305
Not much has changed with the camera,...

00:04.449 --> 00:10.755
...except how you take a photo, find a photo, share a photo.

00:12.017 --> 00:13.465
Oh, Mom's gonna love that one.

00:14.308 --> 00:16.394
Your photos themselves have changed, too.

00:17.695 --> 00:18.799
They move now.

00:19.181 --> 00:21.093
So photos of your friends can do this...

00:22.414 --> 00:24.345
...and the ones of your family can do that...

00:25.027 --> 00:26.147
and your pet photos can do...

00:26.234 --> 00:27.265
Wait, that's your pet?

00:27.616 --> 00:28.359
Uh, yeah.

00:28.471 --> 00:29.002
I dig it.

00:29.550 --> 00:31.879
Oh, now your screen is the flash.

00:32.060 --> 00:33.745
Say cheese... for yourself.

00:34.031 --> 00:36.314
And the camera shoots video in 4K,...

00:37.841 --> 00:40.010
...so everything you shoot looks amazing.

00:41.715 --> 00:43.884
You can even shoot slo-mo in HD.

00:46.015 --> 00:46.499
Nice.

00:47.478 --> 00:48.851
Oh yeah, watch this.

00:51.946 --> 00:53.769
Wait for it.

00:54.455 --> 00:55.259
Splash!

00:56.455 --> 00:58.225
So yeah, that's what's changed.

